{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/echoes_of_exile_gif3.gif?t=1737010672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Echoes of Exile</strong> is a short horror game about discovering a lost mining crew in space. You fly to points of interest and delve into the caves with your drone and flashlight. Your mission, for which you are generally unequipped, is to find the crew of a newly established mining operation. You will be using 'Echo Three', a repurposed ship of the former galactic empire. It wasn't designed for journeys this long or this far out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Send your drone out for recon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One of the few tools you have is a drone which can fit into places inaccessible to humans. It is a useful tool but not without it's limitations.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/echoes_of_exile_gif1.gif?t=1737010672\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unravel the truth about what happened in these caves</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you journey into the depths of the caves to find the crew, you may be able to piece together the events that led to the radio silence.\u00a0 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/echoes_of_exile_gif2.gif?t=1737010672\" />  </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A short horror experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Echoes of Exile is a short game with much to discover. The first playthrough may take 1-2 hours. Those looking for more content will find plenty.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049470/extras/echoes_of_exile_gif4.gif?t=1737010672